ResistanceGA2 1.1.9
---------
* Updated package examples and vignettes to use packed-raster-safe resistance surface handling
* Fixed jl.prep's internal Julia test raster export to work with the current bundled surfaces
* Added a GitHub Actions workflow that runs package checks on substantive pushes and pull requests

ResistanceGA2 1.1.8
---------
* Routed bootstrap, diagnostic, and legacy coefficient MLPE fits through the dyad-aware fitting backend
* Preserved legacy MLPE.lmm numerical behavior while aligning workflow pair metadata with the new MLPE machinery

ResistanceGA2 1.1.7
---------
* Clarified that mlpe and mlpe_data are the preferred standalone MLPE API
* Marked mlpe_rga, MLPE.lmm, and To.From.ID as legacy compatibility helpers in documentation

ResistanceGA2 1.1.6
---------
* Fixed recursive printing of bootstrap tables in all_comb and bootstrap summaries

ResistanceGA2 1.1.5
---------
* Fixed all_comb bootstrap metadata alignment when Null models are included

ResistanceGA2 1.1.4
